Citation.sTitle: Solubilities of p-Aminophenol in Sulfuric acid + Water from (286.15 to 362.80) K
Citation.sAbstract: Using a laser monitoring observation technique, the solubilities of p-aminophenol in sulfuric acid + water have been determined experimentally from 286.15 K to 362.80 K. The experimental data were correlated with the modified Apelblat equation. The calculated results showed good agreement with the experimental data.
